   <title>
      <phrase/>Recommended Hardware Minimums for an Ironic Flat
    Network Model</title>
    <para>When using the <literal>agent_ilo</literal> driver, you should ensure that the most recent iLO
      controller firmware is installed. A recommended minimum for the iLO4 controller is version
      2.30.</para>
   <para>The recommended minimum hardware requirements are based on the  included with the base
      installation and are suitable only for demo environments. For production systems you will want
      to consider your capacity and performance requirements when making decisions about your
      hardware.</para>
